{
  "stem": "10829.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we became-- what do you call it?-- more stubborn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The more they did, and the more stubborn, the more the Haganahs-- we, we went through this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they, they had some bright-- again, in retrospect, they had some bright young people trained.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they knew how to get the blood boiling of all us young kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I mean, we would, we would kill anybody, just all he had to do is tell us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that's how wound up we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, when we got to Hamburg, we were in a DP camp held by the British, actually barbed wired with soldiers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to get powdered eggs and crackers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Red Cross used to come, but no Jewish organizations, to the best of my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was already in '47.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And '47, we stayed down there as a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, Germany offered citizenship to anybody who wanted to go out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I still have a lot of permission to go-- anybody who want to leave the camps could leave the camps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, if you stayed, you were an actual prisoner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In order to leave the camp, you had to sign a-- you got a paper, and you had to sign a paper that you're going out and you're going to settle somewhere in Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And our mission was not to give in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We have to go back to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So kibbutz Dror was stubborn, whatever that was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, we, we stayed there for, for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had the machine guns every 10, 15 feet, wire meshes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had those British soldiers with the skirts-- kilts, and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember as a kid that we used to joke about them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were actually in a prison camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
